import React from 'react'
import { Router, Scene } from 'react-native-router-flux'
import SampleScreen from '../components/SampleeScreen.js'
import LoginScreen from '../components/LoginScreen.js'




// now you can render "App" normally


const Routes = () => (
   <Router>
      <Scene key = "root">

         <Scene key = "LoginScreen" component = {LoginScreen} initial = {true} hideNavBar = {true}/>
         <Scene key = "SampleScreen" component = {SampleScreen} />
         
      </Scene>
   </Router>
)
export default withRouter(Routes)
